#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/index.rst:15
msgid ""
"When rotating or scaling an object or group of vertices/edges/faces, you "
"may want to shift the :term:`pivot point` to make it easier to "
"manipulate an object. Using this selector in the header of any 3D View, "
"you can change the location of the pivot point."
msgstr ""
"当旋转或缩放一个物体或一组顶点/边/面时，可能需要移动 :term:`轴心点` ，以"
"便操作物体。在任何3D视图的标题栏中使用此选择器，可以更改轴心点的位置。"

