#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/index.rst:44
msgid ""
"*Only Origins* is located inside the Pivot Point popover of the 3D View. "
"When this option is enabled, the transformation will change the "
"positions of the object's origins, but will not affect the object itself."
msgstr ""
"*仅原点* 位于3D视图轴心点弹出菜单面板中。当启用此选项，变换将改变物体原点"
"位置，但不会影响物体本身。"

